    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Order containing around 21 species in one family possessing several thousand short, smooth spines that  densely cover a short, stocky body except for the underside, legs, face, and ears.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
